{"tid":2198103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【陳志全私人檢控郭偉強案】 律政司考慮是否介入 要求押後6星期審 陳志全反對","createTime":"2020-09-11T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T07:05:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c14bd7708da1f8bd6e9bfe108b03e1a653d3589c","tid":2198103,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/119118321_3391804897532680_469411264928956325_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=ZFpAt5iM9IYAX8CTM69&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;tp=7&amp;oh=135229d77afdbdb46a2a3938f15cf766&amp;oe=5F806D9C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F119118321_3391804897532680_469411264928956325_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DZFpAt5iM9IYAX8CTM69%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26tp%3D7%26oh%3D135229d77afdbdb46a2a3938f15cf766%26oe%3D5F806D9C&h=52653fec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳志全（慢必）&middot; 1 hr &middot; <br />\n <br />\n剛收到通知，律政司要求法庭押後審理郭偉強案六個星期，以便有更多時間考慮是否介入我的私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n本人反對押後案件，法庭在六月初發出傳票，至今已經超過三個月，律政司應有充足時間考慮是否介入。上次上庭，辯方亦以等候律政司決定及立法會選舉為理，要求押後審訊至下星期一（14/09/2020）。其後選舉被取消，再無藉口拖延，故希望法庭能如期審理此案。<br />\n<br />\n支持「慢必工作室」<a href=\"http://www.patreon.com/slowbeat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fslowbeat&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=413338bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.patreon.com/slowbeat</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chanchichuen/photos/a.581965515183313/3391804894199347/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchanchichuen%2Fphotos%2Fa.581965515183313%2F3391804894199347%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=0fa80874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chanchichuen/photos/a.581965515183313/3391804894199347/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"472340d2afae8da0adc92c5f2660df93c496015f","tid":2198103,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2149c557b79556ed41aa1bdcc7622e5118e73653","tid":2198103,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"劣症屍: 證據不足"},{"pid":"f9ec9513d535a4fe898f2147c3fe704eeba28f74","tid":2198103,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"472340d2afae8da0adc92c5f2660df93c496015f","tid":2198103,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c144a932c872c896a5b4b9f27423d263ff22a540","tid":2198103,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e90ccc1e23ddbb049f10adbd78ccd7f97c0ee2a","tid":2198103,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2149c557b79556ed41aa1bdcc7622e5118e73653","tid":2198103,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"劣症屍: 證據不足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ban